者要求不高，不用很强壮就能用，顶多续航时间短一些。 只要战术配合恰当，同等成本投入的前提下，大盾对重甲的胜率应该更高啊。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-606e21e4680593bfb3f63b03c9265965_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/667533938"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I7pfp+ZDhxo59EAMaCTExMDYxODU5MiDivay3BjAAOF5AGnIJNjY3NTMzOTM4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1726996184.607730", "card_id": "Q_646471658", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 101}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "猫咪会故意和自己的主人「夹子音」吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-805f59845f99b21cf771798ace4de14b_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/646471658"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI7pfp+ZDhxo59EAMaCTEwNTkzODA4NiDVsoGvBjAAOMMBQBtyCTY0NjQ3MTY1OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1726996184.608293", "card_id": "Q_667801546", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 365}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待赵丽颖凭借《风吹半夏》中许半夏一角获得第 34 届飞天奖优秀女演员？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "优秀女演员奖：赵丽颖《风吹半夏》 优秀女演员提名： 唐嫣 《繁花》 杨蓉 《大山的女儿》 刘琳 《父辈的荣耀》 李庚希 《超越》《漫长的季节》 ​​​ 而且赵丽颖《幸福到万家》也被提名了！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-87cd36d3c4c8ea6991f5f92a6797aafe_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/667801546"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI7pfp+ZDhxo59EAMaCTExMDY3ODMxNSCCmLu3BjAAOKoDQBxyCTY2NzgwMTU0NngAq